dcterms:creator: E. Olejarczyk
W. Jernajczyk
dcterms:description: This dataset consists of EEG recordings from 14 patients with schizophrenia and 14 age-matched healthy control subjects, collected during an eyes-closed resting state for 15 minutes at a sampling rate of 250 Hz.
dcterms:title: Dataset collected by the Institute of Psychiatry and Neurology in Warsaw, Poland
